long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Choose some key words from a network call and replace them. Adding for example original domainA.com and replaced domainB.com the extension will lookup network calls with domainA.com in the URL and replace the text with domainB.com.
In this context domainB.com would display instead of domainA.com.
